data.content:
noun
[noncount] the time in the evening when the largest number of people are watching television
The program is being shown during prime time.
a prime-time program
the television shows that are on during prime time
He's the best actor in prime time.
chiefly US informal :the highest or most difficult level of use
This software isn't ready for prime time. [=it is not yet good enough to be used; it has problems that need to be corrected]

Danh từ
giờ cao điểm (có nhiều người nghe phát thanh, xem truyền hình nhất)
